featured.text: Your dog could fall into one of nine categories: Ace, Stargazer, Maverick, Charmer, Socialite, Protodog, Einstein, Expert, or Renaissance Dog.

definition.zh_def: 原始犬類，指的是犬類的早期祖先或前身。
definition.en_def: A protodog is an early ancestor or precursor of modern dogs.
definition.example: The protodog is believed to have lived thousands of years ago, before the domestication of wolves.
